'''''Naughty Ones''''' is a jump-and-run [[platform game]] for the [[Amiga]] and [[Amiga CD32]]. It was released by Interactivision in early 1994. It was programmed by Jacob Gorm Hansen (Paleface) and the graphics were done by Henrik Mikkelsen (Seen), both from the demo group [[Melon Dezign]].

