[[File:Zendmast Ugchelen 2013.jpg|thumb|150px|Transmission tower Ugchelen (2013)]] '''Zendstation Ugchelen''' is the designation of a facility for FM- and TV-broadcasting at [[Ugchelen]], [[Netherlands]]. Zendstation Ugchelen uses as [[transmission tower]] a 142 metre high free standing [[lattice tower]] built in 1959.
